defaultiv) Raises standards – 
defaultR
defaulteforms of the school system must be designed to ensure that 
defaultall pupils are able to access high quality, engaging and relevant leaning opportunities
default that secure the highest possible levels of pupil progress and achievement
default.
default&#xa0;
defaultv) Union recognition – 
defaultApproaches to reform must 
defaultensure that workforce unions a
defaultre properly represented to enable 
